com.github.peterbencze.serritor.internal.util

Class FunctionalReentrantReadWriteLock

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.concurrent.locks.ReentrantReadWriteLock
      • com.github.peterbencze.serritor.internal.util.FunctionalReentrantReadWriteLock
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, ReadWriteLock

    public final class FunctionalReentrantReadWriteLock
extends ReentrantReadWriteLock
    An implementation of ReentrantReadWriteLock that adds the possibility of specifying actions (in a functional manner) which are executed under the lock.
    See Also:
